=AD)</h3><p data-path-to-node=3D"4">Currently, your <code data-path-to-node=
=3D"4" data-index-in-node=3D"16">create_trunk_plane</code> bakes the hip sk=
irt, chest, and head onto a single 260x320 surface. We must split this into=
