trix tracking of the environment from the asset frames of the actor.</p><p =
data-path-to-node=3D"1">The SNES hardware could not dynamically rotate or s=
cale individual sprites. It could only perform those complex affine transfo=
rmations on a single, flat background layer=E2=80=94a hardware feature know=
